{"tid":1300770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大女考見習督察想做一姐 唔肯評論逃犯條例","createTime":"2019-07-09T12:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T12:01:11.000Z","uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":190,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"71cdd0c0943a689ae0890dd0526ec7a4a73a0de7","tid":1300770,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8V4wQ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8V4wQ2.png&h=1d89da10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警隊今日在警務總部舉行「警察招募日」，共收到2,010份申請，當中800人申請見習督察職位，1,113人申請做警員，另有97人申請做輔警。當中見習督察競爭最激烈，約40人爭1個位。有投考見習督察的應徵者笑言「想做一姐」，被問到近日時事，如《逃犯條例》修訂等，她則指「作為一個學生唔方便評論。」港隊田徑隊前隊員盧嘉琳亦希望投考見習督察，以機場特警工作最有興趣，因「佢哋套深藍色制服特別有型」。<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ppagBTIXYnI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FppagBTIXYnI&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7JB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=0cd11664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ppagBTIXYnI</a>"},{"pid":"c4a75466aa422e2352d0008f9db2acadcfe6f3c4","tid":1300770,"uid":3302,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"相由心生"},{"pid":"bc6b53dbb079669ac103904689f4b588f9bee756","tid":1300770,"uid":236414,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"好樣衰"},{"pid":"3391adb2c9405f40f7f32d6d3d13965c9918fac7","tid":1300770,"uid":209225,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:46:12.000Z","msg":"對你好失望<br />\n原來你係$0.3"},{"pid":"2e50a1c1e771a8b44e8de58e3d6b1c01fa317ba9","tid":1300770,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"心果句 著速龍衫打學生哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4652d1f0cadcd15ff1cf56167ef4968282ceaf14","tid":1300770,"uid":3241,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:46:26.000Z","msg":"用個妓字已經唔能夠去形容此女"},{"pid":"9d513845c3cf85ad5e99d2c34139dac242